CustomField.description: Can be used to indicate that the student Contact's record is subject to Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act requirements, without displaying the details of that information.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Indica si el registro de la persona está sujeto a los estándares de Health Insurance Portability (Portabilidad de seguros médicos) y Accountability Act (Ley de responsabilidad).
CustomField.label: HIPAA
